msgid "Advanced Settings"
msgstr "Socruithe chun cinn"

msgid "Album art names"
msgstr "Ainmneacha ealaíne albam"

msgid "Allow wide links"
msgstr "Ceadaigh naisc leathana"

msgid "Announced UUID"
msgstr "UUID fógartha"

msgid "Announced model number"
msgstr "Uimhir mhúnla fógartha"

msgid "Announced serial number"
msgstr "Sraithuimhir fógartha"

msgid "Browse directory"
msgstr "Brabhsáil eolaire"

msgid "Database directory"
msgstr "Eolaire bunachar sonraí"

msgid "Enable"
msgstr "Cumasaigh"

msgid "Enable TIVO"
msgstr "Cumasaigh TIVO"

msgid "Enable inotify"
msgstr "Cumasaigh inotify"

msgid "Friendly name"
msgstr "Ainm cairdiúil"

msgid "General Settings"
msgstr "Socruithe Ginearálta"

msgid "Grant access to minidlna status and configuration"
msgstr "Deonaigh rochtain ar stádas agus cumraíocht minidlna"

msgid "Interfaces"
msgstr "Comhéadain"

msgid "Media directories"
msgstr "Eolaire meáin"

msgid ""
"MiniDLNA is server software with the aim of being fully compliant with DLNA/"
"UPnP-AV clients."
msgstr ""
"Is bogearraí freastalaí é MiniDLNA a bhfuil sé mar aidhm aige a bheith "
"lánchomhlíontach le cliaint DLNA/UPnP-AV."

msgid ""
"Model number the miniDLNA daemon will report to clients in its XML "
"description."
msgstr ""
"Uimhir mhúnla a thuairisceoidh an deamhan miniDLNA do chliaint ina chur síos "
"XML."

msgid "Music"
msgstr "Ceol"

msgid "Network interfaces to serve."
msgstr "Comhéadain líonra chun freastal."

msgid "Notify interval"
msgstr "Eatramh fógra"

msgid "Notify interval in seconds."
msgstr "Cuir an t-eatramh in iúl i soicindí."

msgid "Pictures"
msgstr "Pictiúir"

msgid "Port"
msgstr "Port"

msgid "Port for HTTP (descriptions, SOAP, media transfer) traffic."
msgstr "Port le haghaidh tráchta HTTP (cur síos, gallúnach, aistriú meán)."

msgid "Presentation URL"
msgstr "URL cur i láthair"

msgid "Root container"
msgstr "Coimeádán fréimhe"

msgid ""
"Serial number the miniDLNA daemon will report to clients in its XML "
"description."
msgstr ""
"Sraithuimhir a thuairisceoidh an deamhan miniDLNA do chliaint ina chur síos "
"XML."

msgid ""
"Set this if you want to customize the name that shows up on your clients."
msgstr ""
"Socraigh é seo más mian leat an t-ainm a thaispeánann do chliaint a "
"shaincheapadh."

msgid ""
"Set this if you would like to specify the directory where you want MiniDLNA "
"to store its database and album art cache."
msgstr ""
"Socraigh é seo más mian leat an t-eolaire a shonrú inar mian leat MiniDLNA a "
"bhunachar sonraí agus a thaisce ealaíne albam a stóráil."

msgid ""
"Set this to allow serving content outside the media root (via symlinks)."
msgstr ""
"Socraigh é seo chun go bhféadfar ábhar a riar lasmuigh d'fhréamh na meán "
"(trí shimplí)."

msgid ""
"Set this to enable inotify monitoring to automatically discover new files."
msgstr ""
"Socraigh é seo chun monatóireacht inotify a chumasú chun comhaid nua a "
"aimsiú go huathoibríoch."

msgid ""
"Set this to enable support for streaming .jpg and .mp3 files to a TiVo "
"supporting HMO."
msgstr ""
"Socraigh é seo chun tacaíocht a thabhairt do chomhaid .jpg agus .mp3 a "
"shruthú chuig HMO tacaíochta TiVo."

msgid ""
"Set this to strictly adhere to DLNA standards. This will allow server-side "
"downscaling of very large JPEG images, which may hurt JPEG serving "
"performance on (at least) Sony DLNA products."
msgstr ""
"Socraigh é seo chun cloí go docht le caighdeáin DLNA. Ceadóidh sé seo "
"íomhánna JPEG an-mhór a ísliú ar thaobh an fhreastalaí, rud a d’fhéadfadh "
"feidhmíocht riartha JPEG ar (a laghad) táirgí Sony DLNA a ghortú."

msgid ""
"Set this to the directory you want scanned. If you want to restrict the "
"directory to a specific content type, you can prepend the type ('A' for "
"audio, 'V' for video, 'P' for images), followed by a comma, to the directory "
"(eg. A,/mnt/media/Music). Multiple directories can be specified."
msgstr ""
"Socraigh é seo chuig an eolaire is mian leat a scanadh. Más mian leat an t-"
"eolaire a shrianadh go cineál ábhair ar leith, is féidir leat an cineál ('A' "
"le haghaidh fuaime, 'V' le haghaidh físeáin, 'P' le haghaidh íomhánna), agus "
"camóg ina dhiaidh sin, a ligean ar an eolaire (m.sh. A. ,/mnt/meáin/Ceol). "
"Is féidir eolairí iolracha a shonrú."

msgid "Specify the path to the MiniSSDPd socket."
msgstr "Sonraigh an cosán go dtí an soicéad MiniSSDPd."

msgid "Standard container"
msgstr "Coimeádán caighdeánach"

msgid "Status"
msgstr "Stádas"

msgid "Strict to DLNA standard"
msgstr "Go docht le caighdeán DLNA"

msgid ""
"The miniDLNA service is active, serving %d audio, %d video and %d image "
"files."
msgstr ""
"Tá an tseirbhís miniDLNA gníomhach, ag freastal ar %d fuaime, %d físeán agus "
"%d comhaid íomhá."

msgid "The miniDLNA service is not running."
msgstr "Níl an tseirbhís miniDLNA ag rith."

msgid "This is a list of file names to check for when searching for album art."
msgstr ""
"Seo liosta ainmneacha comhaid le seiceáil nuair a bhíonn ealaín albam á "
"chuardach."

msgid "Video"
msgstr "Físeán"

msgid "miniDLNA"
msgstr "miniDLNA"

msgid "miniDLNA Status"
msgstr "Stádas miniDLNA"

msgid "miniSSDP socket"
msgstr "soicéad miniSSDP"
